title: Almighty Master
description: Almighty Master Manhua Let’s take a look at our young hero here, who was born and entered the world of Martial Arts. There’s nothing that he cannot do! Music, chess, medicine or even culinary arts. Pretending to be the weakest while he is the strongest. Women from left to right. Look at how an orphan rises. An orphan who will solve numerous cases and who will become the master of the city! The Peak Master of the City โคตรพยัคฆ์โลกาวินาศ 全能高手
